  "hadith0": "\"Allahyn in soyyan amallary, az hem bolsa, yzygiderli edilen amallardy.\"\n— Buhari we Muslim",
  "hadith1": "\"Basaryp biljek amallarynyzdan tutunyn, cunki in gowy amallar az bolsa-da yzygiderli edilenlerdir.\"\n— Ibn Maje",
  "hadith2": "\"Adam ogly olende, amallary uc zatdan basga kesilyer: dowamly sadaka, peydaly ylym ya-da onun ucin doga edyan salyh perzent.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith3": "\"Kim iki salkyn namazy (Ertir we Ikindi) okasa, jennete girer.\"\n— Buhari",
  "hadith4": "\"Allah sizin dasky gorkuinize ya-da baylygynyza dal, yureginize we amallarynyza sereder.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith5": "\"Adamlaryn in gowusy, adamlara in peydaly bolanlardyr.\"\n— Darakutni",
  "hadith6": "\"Ansatlasdyryn, kynlasdyrman; busunji habar berin, adamlary gayyrmang.\"\n— Buhari",
  "hadith7": "\"Kim ylym gozlap yola cykyar, Allah onun ucin jennete baryan yoly ansatlasdyrar.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith8": "\"Sadaka baylygy azaltmaz.\"\n— Muslim",
  "hadith9": "\"Guyyli momin, ejiz mominden gowusy hem Allaha has soygulisidir, her ikisinde hem hayyr bardyr.\"\n— Muslim",
